<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Quality Digital Services</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset and base */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }
    body{
      /* height: 100%; */
      background-color: #f2f4ff;
    }

    /* Wrapper to center everything vertically and horizontally */
    .page-wrapper {
      min-height: 100vh; /* full viewport height */
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center; /* vertical center */
      align-items: center;     /* horizontal center */
      padding: 20px;
      gap: 30px; /* spacing between header, main, button */
    }

    header {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 10px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .logo img {
      width: 400px;
      height: 100px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .logo span {
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .logo span b {
      color: #f90;
    }

    nav a {
      margin-left: 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #ff6600;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 20px;
    }


    .main-container {
      max-width: 700px;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #e8f1ff;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .app-logo {
      width: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #c60000;
    }

    h3 {
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }

    ul, ol {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    button {
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background-color: #f57c00;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      font-size: 16px;
      width: 200px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(245, 124, 0, 0.4);
    }
    button:hover {
      background-color: #e06b00;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  
     <header class="header">
    <a href="/dashboard"><div class="logo">
      <img src="image/Hiring_Poster1Artboard_8@4x[1](1).png"></div></a>
    <nav class="nav-links">
      <a href="/dashboard">Home</a>
      <a href="/careerneed">Careers</a>
      <a href="/logoutneed">Logout</a>
    </nav>
  </header>
<div class="page-wrapper">
    <main class="main-container">
      <section class="info-card">
        <img src="image/HDFC Rupay Credit Card.png" alt="Airtel Logo" class="app-logo"/>
        <h2>HDFC UPI RuPay Credit Card – Key Benefits Promoted by Quality Digital Services</h2>
        <h3>Benefits:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Make UPI payments using this credit card and earn cashpoints.</li>
          <li>Enjoy up to 50 days of interest-free credit from the date of purchase.</li>
          <li>Earn 3% Cashpoints on groceries, supermarket, dining spends, and all PayZapp transactions.</li>
          <li>Earn 2% Cashpoints on utility bill payments.</li>
          <li>Earn 1% Cashpoints on other spends (excluding rent, wallet loads, EMI, fuel, and government categories).</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Whom to Promote? (Eligibility):</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Age: 21 to 60 years</li>
          <li>Minimum Income: ₹25,000/month (Salaried)</li>
          <li>Minimum ITR: ₹6,00,000 per annum (Self-Employed)</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>How It Works:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Visit the credit card page and select HDFC UPI RuPay Credit Card.</li>
          <li>Click on the ‘Link Your Card to Swiggy’ button at the bottom (if applicable).</li>
          <li>Enter your registered mobile number and submit the OTP received.</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Terms & Conditions:</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Cashpoints earned on UPI payments and utility spends as described.</li>
          <li>Up to 50 days of interest-free credit from purchase date.</li>
          <li>Earning rates may change without prior notice; always stay updated.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>
    </main>

    <button onclick="location.href='/ChRB'">Click here to Continue</button>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
